{"tid":1765022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係冷氣軍師，入黎屌我啦","createTime":"2019-12-01T14:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T17:15:22.000Z","uid":218298,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed860a70e193b6fad936e88dfc88905ac982088","tid":1765022,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"入到黎唔好屌住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下完下面先屌<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇完個post話唔好打藍絲個頭，我心諗：屌啊，禁多前線巴絲比人捉既捉、打既打，而家打下個頭就搞分化<br />\n<br />\n但老老實實，打頭真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全係失敗中既失敗，因為我岩岩諗到個新方法，直情可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嚴懲呢班藍絲同鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位勇武 除左唔好打得禁細力，綁唔綁就你地諗先<br />\n最重要係幫佢<span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩/蒙面、換黑衫</span>到時班狗一衝 唔好推佢地去送死<br />\n<br />\n註：如果係狗就<strong>請勿</strong>拎走佢個狗牌，以免班狗識別唔到佢地既自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拿 好橋勿屌"},{"pid":"de4516b5f9369694396d086fd46e5880acb4fd38","tid":1765022,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb83c67498b3a809feb6fc99a926dbd1ab9ec84","tid":1765022,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"70a984f8d3eecb6588e4135b4d635b38e61313fb","tid":1765022,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"6609668637632468f2fbea99f69edaae0ea3aff8","tid":1765022,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"有冇時間搞咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef96a07fc64dd65fd185542d5222958aa85da